observations.recommendation:
We recommended and the Local Chief Executive agreed to - 

a.	prepare/submit a request to the EMB-DENR for an extension of time in the implementation of the project, pending the acquisition of land suitable for the purpose;



b.	direct the MENRO and the Municipal Engineer to expedite the search for suitable location of the project in order to facilitate the implementation/ establishment of permanent MRF for the municipality;

c.	in case the request for extension of time is not granted, file a request for authority with the EMB-DENR to allow the implementation of the same project in one of the barangays of Licab so that the constituents of the municipality will still be benefited therefrom. 

d.	remind the Heads of the Offices concerned to strictly observe the scheduled implementation of the projects to ensure efficient delivery of public services to the intended beneficiaries and to avoid the recurrence of similar lapses in the future.

We recommended and the Local Chief Executive, the Vice Mayor and the Sanggunian concerned agreed to (a) provide appropriation/funds for the titling of the four (4) lots in the name of the Municipal Government of Licab; 
(b) designate personnel/s who will undertake the titling thereof to ensure the right of ownership over the subject real properties; and 
(c) disclose the lease contract entered into by the Municipality with the Licab Water District on lot item No. 4 in the Notes to FS in conformity with PPSAS No. 1.
